subject: Harness Racing
Horse Racing
lead_paragraph: Tattler’s Jet, a 14-year-old gelding that had been a fan favorite in the Midwest throughout his 12-year career, overcame a poor trip to finish a fast-closing second on Thursday at Monticello Raceway.
